          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/7998136/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_6175608277421306547.png",
                "id": "talent46793",
                "key": "踏辰攝斗",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "踏辰攝斗"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冰翎</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冰翎</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色造成的冰元素傷害+1。（包括角色引發的冰元素擴散傷害）</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/7998136/af48cc3ce2404a2ad32b4632074daafc_8469684845817285838.png",
                "id": "talent33441",
                "key": "仰靈威召將役咒",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "仰靈威召將役咒"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">籙靈</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/7998136/0af9611ff900342f560004bd85d6e766_7317804012673450435.png",
                "id": "talent74548",
                "key": "神女遣靈真訣",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神女遣靈真訣"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此召喚物在場時：</span>敵方角色受到的<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>和<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/7998136/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3271707993383576975.png",
                "id": "talent68855",
                "key": "籙靈",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/7998136/0729bd2530214665f6a30676963e3d6f_1168980292317829875.png",
                "title": "籙靈"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著冰元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到物理或火元素傷害後提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/7998136/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_2154898007800689476.png",
                "id": "talent97816",
                "key": "冰元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6314248466430212525.png",
